profile_positions.description:
My focus area: Kenya, Tanzania and Cambodia focusing on young people, entrepreneurship and employability in the field of agribusiness, ICT and others. 

Main tasks and responsibilities:

- Working on ICS strategy around young people, entrepreneurship and employability;
- Develop new (social business) cases;
- Monitor existing programs and further develop them;
- Connect with several companies and organizations in the Netherlands and abroad to exchange   
  knowledge and to work together within several business cases;
- Write (fundraising) proposals. 

All this in close cooperation with local ICS colleagues and other (local) partners.
